    "body": "## Problem\r\nExpected text for interactive marks is in a separate json file from the tutor file. When the tutor file is updated, line numbers (potentially many) have to be updated in the json file. This is a burden for maintenance and automatic testing.\r\n\r\n## Solution\r\n\r\nPut the expected text inline in the tutor file.\r\n`This is wrong. <==This is right==>`\r\nParse and remove the comments before opening the tutor file so extmarks can be applied.\r\n\r\nAI-assisted: Codex\r\nCloses #38527 ",
    "closed_at": null,
